(1, 'Afia bora', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0.5rem;font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;font-weight: 500;line-height: 1.3;color: rgb(60, 72, 88);font-size: 2rem;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 48px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Nom du projet</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 47px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px\">AFIA BORA est une solution&nbsp;</span>numérique<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px\">&nbsp;efficace au problème de la santé, donnant accès à tous&nbsp; de ses connecter et de bénéficier plus sur ses services.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 47px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px\">Nous utilisons un prix trop bas, adapté à tout le monde d&#39;y consommé sans difficulté.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 95px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 17.12px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 17.12px;font-family: Wingdings\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 17.12px\">Le produit en soit s’est nommé «&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;background: aqua\">Afia bora</span>» qui signifie&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;background: aqua\">bonne santé</span>&nbsp;;</span></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0.5rem;font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;font-weight: 500;line-height: 1.3;color: rgb(60, 72, 88);font-size: 2rem;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 48px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Wingdings;color: windowtext\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span arial=\"\" mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 17.12px\">&nbsp;</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Proposition de valeur unique</span></h2><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: normal\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px\">Permettre l’accès aux Hôpitaux et aux malades de se connecter en grande quantité avec peu de mégas sur la plateforme et faire une meilleure gestion de suivi adéquat et la protection&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700\">électronique</span>&nbsp;des dossiers des malades à l’aide de carnet médical&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700\">électronique</span>&nbsp;couvert par&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-weight: 700\">QRCODE</span>.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0.5rem;font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;font-weight: 500;line-height: 1.3;color: rgb(60, 72, 88);font-size: 2rem;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 48px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family: Wingdings;color: windowtext\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;color: windowtext\">&nbsp;</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box\">Description du projet</span></h2><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 47px;font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;line-height: 36px;color: rgb(60, 72, 88);font-size: 1.5rem;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" color:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;line-height: 28px\">I.1.2.1 Information Générale sur l’application Afia bora</span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 50px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" color:=\"\" background-image:=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">« AFIA BORA » est une plateforme web et mobile de suivi électronique de dossiers de patients par la technologie QRCODE&nbsp;; les informations sensibles des patients et leurs dossiers médicaux sont désormais protégés par&nbsp; un carnet médical électronique&nbsp; couvert par un QRCODE appelé AFIA BORA.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 50px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" color:=\"\" background-image:=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Nous avons remarqué que les malades sont victimes par plusieurs problèmes sanitaires notamment&nbsp;:</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 118px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-family: Symbol\">·<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Mauvaise&nbsp; consultation&nbsp; médicale&nbsp;;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 118px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-family: Symbol\">·<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Manque d’un suivi adéquat de leurs dossiers&nbsp;;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 118px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-family: Symbol\">·<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Perte de temps considérables lors de la recherche de leurs dossiers médicaux et de contretemps&nbsp; liés aux différents rendez-vous avec leurs médecins.</span></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 47px;font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;line-height: 36px;color: rgb(60, 72, 88);font-size: 1.5rem;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" color:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 19px;line-height: 28px\">I.1.2.2 Description détaillée du projet</span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 66px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;text-indent: 28px;line-height: 24px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Nous avons perdu les êtres chers suite aux erreurs médicales et manque d’orientation d’un soin de santé efficace&nbsp;; les patients sont victimes de recevoir un soin de santé auquel ils sont allergiques et nous avons assez perdu de personnes suite à un mauvais traitement&nbsp; de soin de santé.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 0 66px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">La genèse d’idée est la création d’une entreprise permettant de livrer de services technologiques sur la protection sanitaire de la vie des êtres humains.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 1rem;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-left: 71px;text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;background: lime\">Pour pallier contre les erreurs médicales&nbsp; et assurer la garantie sanitaire de patients, la plateforme web dénommée AFIA BORA est venue résoudre les soucis.</span>&nbsp;AFIA BORA permettra aux hôpitaux de créer des comptes et bénéficier plus de nos services notamment&nbsp;:</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 109px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-family: Wingdings\">ü<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Un suivi adéquat et protection électronique des dossiers de malades&nbsp;;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 109px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-family: Wingdings\">ü<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Contrôle efficace de dossiers, des ordonnances et de rendez-vous de chaque malade envers le médecin&nbsp;;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 109px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-family: Wingdings\">ü<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">Un horaire médical électroniquement bien protégé et assistance immédiate au patient en cas de danger qui nécessite un soin de santé immédiat.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 109px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px;font-family: Wingdings\">ü<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">En bref une application web et mobile de gestion entière de l’hôpital assurant notamment&nbsp;:</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 133px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span courier=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">o<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">La gestion de la pharmacie&nbsp;;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 133px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span courier=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">o<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">La gestion de laboratoire</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 133px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span courier=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">o<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">La gestion de leur comptabilité&nbsp;;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 133px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span courier=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">o<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">La gestion de consultation&nbsp;;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0 0 11px 133px;color: rgb(132, 146, 166);font-family: Nunito, sans-serif;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;line-height: 24px\"><span courier=\"\" mso-fareast-font-family:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">o<span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;line-height: 24px\">La gestion&nbsp; et évaluation de traitement de malade ….</span></p><p><br/></p>', 'projet//182bf32661273ad211a23d2d1b8538ae.png', '2022-08-04 11:33:25', '2022-08-04 11:34:52'),
(2, 'Dream ulimaji', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Dream ulimaji est une application web et mobile connectée à un capteur de sol qui renverra les données à l&#39;application dans le but de croitre la productivité agricole, facilitant ainsi&nbsp; au producteur de savoir précisément quand planter les produits agricoles, où les planter et comment les planter en tenant compte de la période et de l&#39;état du sol.&nbsp; Le&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">producteur&nbsp;</span>pourra aussi entrer en discussion sur un forum de cultivateurs pour réduire le plus d&#39;erreurs dans la culture de telle ou telle autre produit agricole afin de maximiser les récoltes. <span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Dream ulimaji permettra aussi&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17.6px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">aux agriculteurs de connaître la météo au quotidien.</span></span></p>', 'projet//4018b860ab2d90187cd24817c0dd1ebb.jpg', '2022-08-04 11:52:47', '2022-08-04 11:52:47');
